{% block pre_content %}
    <!--
    Include this snippet only on the frontpage.
    Testing tool: https://search.google.com/structured-data/testing-tool
    Documentation: https://developers.google.com/search/docs/data-types/sitelinks-searchbox
    -->
    <script type='application/ld+json'>
        {
            "@context": "https://schema.org",
            "@type": "WebSite",
            "@id": "http://my-website-url.com/#website",
            "url": "http://my-website-url.com/",
            "name": "Name of the website",
            "potentialAction": {
                "@type": "SearchAction",
                "target": "http://my-website-url.com/?s={search_term_string}",
                "query-input": "required name=search_term_string"
            }
        }

    </script>
{% endblock %}

{% block content %}
    {% include '../blocks/banner-about.twig' %}
    {% include '../blocks/content-two-column.twig' %}
    <div class="block-plurimum">
        <div class="wrapper">
            <div class="row-col align-center">
                <div class="col-left col-6">
                    <h2 class="title">
                        Plurimum in amicitia amicorum bene suaden
                    </h2>
                    <p class="text-medium">Itaque earum rerum hic tenetur a sapiente delectus, ut aut reiciendis
                        voluptatibus maiores</p>
                    <ul class="list-plurimum">
                        <li>It co-develops and determines with the telecom operator the specified equipment and
                            materials requested for its networks
                        </li>
                        <li>It provides value for money “own label” equipment, small tooling and accessories to its
                            direct clients, the contractors and sub- contractors who install and maintain networks
                        </li>
                        <li>It has developed and maintains more than 10,000 references in constant evolution stored in
                            70,000 sqm for super fast delivery
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="col-right col-6">
                    <div class="include-image">
                        <img src="./assets/images/img-about-ser.jpg" alt="" class="image-right">
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="block-content-two-column column-sm">
        <div class="wrapper">
            <h2 class="title">Plurimum in amicitia amicorum bene suaden</h2>
            <div class="row d-flex">
                <div class="col">
                    <p>Over more than 25 years, ETC Group has forged strong relationships with all levels of the value
                        chain: telecom operators, national specialist telecom contractors, civil engineering groups and
                        local SME subcontractors, bringing unequalled expertise in co-development, sourcing, and
                        procurement of innovative products.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col">
                    <p>The success of ETC Group’s business model lies in its incumbent position as the critical link in
                        the sourcing of product and equipment needs for the full value chain, from the telecom operator
                        who prescribes the products to all the various levels of direct and indirect
                        sub-contractors.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    {% include '../blocks/history-slide.twig' %}
    {% include '../blocks/key-figures.twig' %}
{% endblock %}
